posts.post_title: FS/FT: T205s incl. HOF, SPs, off-backs (prices dropped)
posts.post_content:
Looking to sell or trade these T205s, including some single-prints and many off-backs.
Some of these front/back combinations can be pretty difficult to find.

PayPal f/f only.  
For orders of at least $50 total, prices include shipping (to domestic USA only).
USPS tracked shipping, in bubble mailer for under $100 or Priority Box for $100+.
Less than $50 total, please add $4 shipping.

Prices negotiable, especially for multiple cards.
Please reply to this thread, or PM me here on net54, or email me at mpg1972 (at) gmail[dot]com
"Sold" takes precedence over ongoing negotiations.


I will also trade for items on my Want List at
[url]http://www.net54baseball.com/showthread.php?t=227775[/url]
Net54 references are listed at the bottom of the Want List.


Scans are in this post and the first few replies.
Click on the image to see a larger version.

Some of these cards have creases, paper loss, are miscut, or have other defects.
To my knowledge, these cards aren't trimmed, but I cannot guarantee that.
Note that T205s with American Beauty backs are often factory-cut narrower than other T205s. 
Message me with any specific condition questions.
